\": 252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9374832882302574, \"rank\": 0.06659701679756723, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Photo: Mark Condren  There might be medals in Paris, but home is where the heart is, and that's where boxer Kellie Harrington's \\u00adfamily will be supporting her from as she embarks on her second Olympic journey.\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 522, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 359, \"end\": 364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999973861856742, \"rank\": 2.613821145569055e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That home is on Portland Row in north inner-city Dublin, where the memories are still strong of everyone gathering at dawn in front of a big screen on August 8, 2021, to watch Harrington overcome the challenge of Beatriz Ferreira to win gold in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 540, \"end\": 548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portland_Trail_Blazers\", \"score\": 0.40366397056846604, \"rank\": 0.8075084129132027, \"text\": \"Portland\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portland_Trail_Blazers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portland_Trail_Blazers\"}, {\"begin\": 573, \"end\": 579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"score\": 0.9477404290464455, \"rank\": 0.054334952444579046, \"text\": \"Dublin\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin\"}, {\"begin\": 700, \"end\": 710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_F._Harrington\", \"score\": 0.9354005639817609, \"rank\": 0.0362